divs: Sighting DetailsObserved two star-like objects flying overhead in normal speed toward NE direction of Brea and Yorba Linda at 7:48PM and quickly took out digital camera Nikon P60 Coolpix and video recorded for a short duration of 1'38" until it faded away. No flashing lights had been seen and the first one is brighter than the following one behind. Silence and no other engine noises could be heard. Both husband and wife witnessed.
